All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
ConfigurationManager
The ConfigurationManager class is responsible for managing the plugin's configuration.
GameplayManager
The GameplayManager class is responsible for managing the gameplay of the UHC plugin.
MinecraftColor
The MinecraftColor enum represents different colors used in Minecraft's text formatting.
MinecraftText
The MinecraftText class represents text with optional formatting attributes used in Minecraft.
MinecraftTextBuilder
The MinecraftTextBuilder class is used to construct complex Minecraft-formatted text strings.
PlayerJoinListener
The PlayerJoinListener class is responsible for handling player join events.
PlayerLoginListener
The PlayerLoginListener class is responsible for handling player login events.
TeamManager
The TeamManager class is responsible for managing teams in the plugin.
Title
The Title class represents a title message with optional display duration and fade-in/fade-out effects.
TitleManager
The TitleManager class provides functionality to manage and display titles with optional JSON formatting to players.
TitleManager.BuiltInTitle
An enum containing predefined built-in titles.
UHCConfigCommandExecutor
The UHCConfigCommandExecutor class is responsible for handling the /uhc-config command.
UHCConfigException
A base exception class for handling configuration-related exceptions in the UHC Pantuflas plugin.
UHCConfigTabCompleter
The UHCConfigTabCompleter class provides tab-completion suggestions for the /uhc-config command.
UHCConfigUnknownOptionException
An exception thrown when attempting to access or modify an unknown configuration option within a section.
UHCConfigUnknownSectionException
An exception thrown when attempting to access or modify an unknown configuration section.
UHCConfigWrongValueException
 
UHCConfigWrongValueTypeException
An exception thrown when a configuration option has a value of the wrong data type.
UHCGameMode
The UHCGameMode enum represents different game modes available for Ultra Hardcore (UHC) matches.
UHCPantuflas
UHCPantuflas is a Minecraft plugin that allows players to create and customize "Ultra Hardcore" (UHC) game mode matches on a Minecraft server.
UHCTeam
The UHCTeam class represents a team in the UHC plugin.
UHCTeamCommandExecutor
The UHCTeamCommandExecutor class handles team-related commands for the UHC plugin.
UHCTeamException
The UHCTeamException class is a custom exception that can be thrown to indicate errors related to UHC teams.
UHCTeamSizeExceededException
The UHCTeamSizeExceededException class represents an exception thrown when the team size limit is exceeded.
UHCTeamTabCompleter
The UHCTeamTabCompleter class provides tab-completion suggestions for UHCTeam related commands.
UnknownUHCTeamException
The UnknownUHCTeamException class represents an exception thrown when attempting to access or manipulate a team that does not exist.
